# Not to do list api

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000/api/v1/tasks

### POST the task list
POST {{baseUrl}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "task": "Go to the gym",
    "hr": 1
}

### Get request
GET {{baseUrl}}

### Update the task list
PUT {{baseUrl}}


### Delete the task list
DELETE {{baseUrl}}